<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Blog | Zero Method</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Tips, insights, and strategies for using AI to boost productivity." />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --obsidian: #0A0A0F;
      --void: #141418;
      --gold: #F59E0B;
      --amber: #FBBF24;
      --white: #FFFFFF;
      --smoke: #A1A1AA;
      --slate: #71717A;
      --ink: #27272A;
    }
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      background: var(--obsidian);
      color: var(--white);
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    .gradient-text {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--white) 0%, var(--smoke) 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
    .card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 24px;
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--white);
      display: block;
    }
    .card:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--amber), var(--gold));
      color: #000;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px -10px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4);
    }
    /* Blog list styling */
    .blog-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .blog-card {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .blog-card {
        flex-direction: row;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 24px;
      }
    }
    .blog-meta {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      min-width: 140px;
    }
    .blog-content {
      flex: 1;
    }
    .blog-title {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--white);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .blog-excerpt {
      color: var(--smoke);
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }
    .arrow {
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 bg-[#0A0A0F]/90 backdrop-blur-xl border-b border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-white flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-black font-bold text-sm">0</span>
        </div>
        <span class="font-semibold text-white">Zero Method</span>
      </a>
      
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
        <a href="/" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-1">
          <span>←</span> Back to Home
        </a>
        <a href="/product" class="btn-primary text-sm px-5 py-2.5">Get Started</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Blog Content -->
  <section class="min-h-screen pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-amber-400 mb-4">Blog</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight gradient-text">Zero Method Blog</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4">Tips, insights, and strategies for using AI to boost productivity.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="blog-list">
        <a href="/blog/ai-market-week-1" class="card blog-card hover:border-amber-500/30">
          <div class="blog-meta">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 text-xs text-amber-400 whitespace-nowrap">Analysis</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">5 min</span>
          </div>
          <div class="blog-content">
            <div class="blog-title">AI Market This Week: What Actually Matters</div>
            <div class="blog-excerpt">The signal in the noise — what professionals should actually pay attention to this week.</div>
          </div>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/blog/the-5-minute-email" class="card blog-card hover:border-blue-500/30">
          <div class="blog-meta">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 text-xs text-blue-400 whitespace-nowrap">Email</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">4 min</span>
          </div>
          <div class="blog-content">
            <div class="blog-title">The 5-Minute Email That Actually Works</div>
            <div class="blog-excerpt">A prompt we tested 47 times before including it in the pack.</div>
          </div>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/blog/welcome-to-zero-method" class="card blog-card hover:border-emerald-500/30">
          <div class="blog-meta">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/10 text-xs text-emerald-400 whitespace-nowrap">Welcome</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">3 min</span>
          </div>
          <div class="blog-content">
            <div class="blog-title">Welcome to Zero Method</div>
            <div class="blog-excerpt">Why we built this and what makes us different.</div>
          </div>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</body>
</html>